Mart B. Strater, Respondent, v. Nicholas A. Strater, Appellant. Arlen G. Loselle, Respondent, v. Nicholas A. Strater, Appellant. Roger V. Pugh, Jr., Respondent, v. Nicholas A. Strater, Appellant. Submitted June 8, 1964; decided June 10, 1964. *875Herschel E. Sparks, Jr., for motions.

No one opposed.

Motions granted and appeals dismissed, with costs and $10 costs of motions, upon the ground that the orders appealed from do not finally determine the actions within the meaning of the Constitution.
